        <div class="roadmap-dot absolute -left-10 top-1"></div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">
          Q3 2026 · Planned
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-zinc-400">ERP &amp; Payments</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          SAP invoice ingestion, CSV bank statement parsing, automated reconciliation, bulk payment orchestration, and external payment rail integration.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-2 mt-4 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/3 border border-white/5 rounded font-mono text-[8px] text-zinc-700 uppercase">
            SAP
          </span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/3 border border-white/5 rounded font-mono text-[8px] text-zinc-700 uppercase">
            Reconciliation
          </span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/3 border border-white/5 rounded font-mono text-[8px] text-zinc-700 uppercase">
            Payments
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="roadmap-dot absolute -left-10 top-1"></div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">
          Q4 2026 · Planned
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-zinc-400">Intelligence &amp; Forecasting</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          AI anomaly detection (BERT + Z-score), 30-day liquidity forecasting, vendor sentiment analysis, 6-metric compliance scorecard, and automated remediation recommendations.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-2 mt-4 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/3 border border-white/5 rounded font-mono text-[8px] text-zinc-700 uppercase">
            AI Detection
          </span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/3 border border-white/5 rounded font-mono text-[8px] text-zinc-700 uppercase">
            Forecasting
          </span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-white/3 border border-white/5 rounded font-mono text-[8px] text-zinc-700 uppercase">
