      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
<!-- ── Security ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="security" class="py-32 px-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-serif italic mb-4">
        Security by <span class="text-emerald-400">Design</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Institutional buyers don't ask if it's secure. They ask how. Here's how.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
      <div class="elite-card p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-400/10 border border-emerald-400/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <i data-lucide="fingerprint" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">WebAuthn / FIDO2</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          Biometric authentication with hardware-bound credentials. No passwords stored. No phishing surface. Step-up required for every high-value transfer.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="elite-card p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-400/10 border border-emerald-400/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <i data-lucide="layers" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Event-Sourced Immutability</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          Every state change is an immutable, timestamped event. Nothing is updated or deleted. The audit trail is the source of truth, not a secondary log.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="elite-card p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-400/10 border border-emerald-400/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <i data-lucide="shield" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Secrets in Vault</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          HashiCorp Vault manages all secrets in production. Zero credentials in environment variables or config files. Dynamic secrets rotated on every deploy.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="elite-card p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-400/10 border border-emerald-400/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <i data-lucide="users" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Separation of Duties</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          Role-based access with real-time SoD conflict detection. A user cannot be both trader and approver. Conflicts are flagged immediately, not at audit time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="elite-card p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-400/10 border border-emerald-400/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <i data-lucide="eye" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Full Observability</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          OpenTelemetry distributed tracing, structured logs shipped to Loki, Prometheus metrics with Grafana dashboards. Every request is traceable end-to-end.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="elite-card p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-400/10 border border-emerald-400/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <i data-lucide="server" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Distributed Fault Tolerance</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          Multi-node Erlang cluster with Horde for distributed process management. HAProxy load balancing. No single point of failure in the application layer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
<!-- ── CTA ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-32 px-4 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-emerald-500/8 blur-[100px] rounded-full pointer-events-none">
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif italic mb-6 relative">
      Ready to see <span class="text-emerald-400">Equinox</span> in action?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg font-light mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Join finance teams at multinationals who are replacing manual treasury processes with intelligent, auditable infrastructure.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
      <a
        href={~p"/register"}
        class="btn-liquid bg-emerald-400 text-obsidian px-10 py-5 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase font-bold shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(52,211,153,0.3)]"
      >
        <span class="relative z-10">Request Private Access</span>
        <div class="liquid-bg"></div>
      </a>
      <a
        href="mailto:contact@equinox.io"
        class="btn-liquid px-10 py-5 border border-white/20 hover:border-emerald-400 transition-colors font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-white"
      >
        <span class="relative z-10">Talk to Sales</span>
        <div class="liquid-bg bg-white/5"></div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<!-- ── Footer ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<footer class="border-t border-white/5 py-16 px-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
